
<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">

<div class="container">
  <h1 >Pick An Interest</h1>
<div class="container text-center">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1707343848552-893e05dba6ac?w=400&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDF8MHxzZWFyY2h8OHx8dHJhdmVsfGVufDB8fDB8fHww" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Travel and Exploration</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Travel opens our minds to diverse cultures and experiences, from ancient ruins to bustling cities. It fosters personal growth, global understanding, and connections with people from different backgrounds.</p>
                    <a href="/travel" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1445985543470-41fba5c3144a?w=400&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8N3x8TXVzaWN8ZW58MHx8MHx8fDA%3D" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Music and Arts</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Music and art express emotions and creativity, transcending cultural boundaries. Whether through a song or painting, they inspire thought, joy, and a shared sense of humanity.</p>
                    <a href="/arts" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486286701208-1d58e9338013?w=400&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8NHx8Zm9vdGJhbGx8ZW58MHx8MHx8fDA%3D" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Sports and Fitness</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Sports are essential for physical health, teamwork, and resilience. Whether through individual activities team sports like soccer, staying active reduces stress and builds a sense of community and belonging.</p>
                    <a href="/sport" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464226184884-fa280b87c399?w=400&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8NHx8Rm9vZHxlbnwwfHwwfHx8MA%3D%3D" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Food and Cuisine</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Food reflects cultural identity and traditions. From street food to gourmet dishes, culinary experiences connect us and enrich our understanding of different regions.</p>
                    <a href="/food" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</div>


